{"tha-ap500:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap500:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap500:0.3":"8 Pulinathupiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap500:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap500:1.2":"yamako nama pabbato; ","tha-ap500:1.3":"Assamo sukato mayham, ","tha-ap500:1.4":"pannasala sumapita. ","tha-ap500:2.1":"Narado nama namena, ","tha-ap500:2.2":"jatilo uggatapano; ","tha-ap500:2.3":"Catuddasasahassani, ","tha-ap500:2.4":"sissa paricaranti mam. ","tha-ap500:3.1":"Patisallinako santo, ","tha-ap500:3.2":"evam cintesaham tada; ","tha-ap500:3.3":"‘Sabbo jano mam pujeti, ","tha-ap500:3.4":"naham pujemi kincanam. ","tha-ap500:4.1":"Na me ovadako atthi, ","tha-ap500:4.2":"vatta koci na vijjati; ","tha-ap500:4.3":"Anacariyupajjhayo, ","tha-ap500:4.4":"vane vasam upemaham. ","tha-ap500:5.1":"Upasamano yamaham, ","tha-ap500:5.2":"garucittam upatthahe; ","tha-ap500:5.3":"So me acariyo natthi, ","tha-ap500:5.4":"vanavaso niratthako. ","tha-ap500:6.1":"Ayagam me gavesissam, ","tha-ap500:6.2":"garum bhavaniyam tatha; ","tha-ap500:6.3":"Savassayo vasissami, ","tha-ap500:6.4":"na koci garahissati’. ","tha-ap500:7.1":"Uttanakula nadika, ","tha-ap500:7.2":"supatittha manorama; ","tha-ap500:7.3":"Samsuddhapulinakinna, ","tha-ap500:7.4":"avidure mamassamam. ","tha-ap500:8.1":"Nadim amarikam nama, ","tha-ap500:8.2":"upagantvanaham tada; ","tha-ap500:8.3":"Samvaddhayitva pulinam, ","tha-ap500:8.4":"akam pulinacetiyam. ","tha-ap500:9.1":"Ye te ahesum sambuddha, ","tha-ap500:9.2":"bhavantakarana muni; ","tha-ap500:9.3":"Tesam etadiso thupo, ","tha-ap500:9.4":"tam nimittam karomaham. ","tha-ap500:10.1":"Karitva pulinam thupam, ","tha-ap500:10.2":"sovannam mapayim aham; ","tha-ap500:10.3":"Sonnakinkanipupphani, ","tha-ap500:10.4":"sahasse tini pujayim. ","tha-ap500:11.1":"Sayam patam namassami, ","tha-ap500:11.2":"vedajato katanjali; ","tha-ap500:11.3":"Sammukha viya sambuddham, ","tha-ap500:11.4":"vandim pulinacetiyam. ","tha-ap500:12.1":"Yada kilesa jayanti, ","tha-ap500:12.2":"vitakka gehanissita; ","tha-ap500:12.3":"Sarami sukatam thupam, ","tha-ap500:12.4":"paccavekkhami tavade. ","tha-ap500:13.1":"Upanissaya viharam, ","tha-ap500:13.2":"satthavaham vinayakam; ","tha-ap500:13.3":"Kilese samvaseyyasi, ","tha-ap500:13.4":"na yuttam tava marisa. ","tha-ap500:14.1":"Saha avajjite thupe, ","tha-ap500:14.2":"garavam hoti me tada; ","tha-ap500:14.3":"Kuvitakke vinodesim, ","tha-ap500:14.4":"nago tuttattito yatha. ","tha-ap500:15.1":"Evam viharamanam mam, ","tha-ap500:15.2":"maccurajabhimaddatha; ","tha-ap500:15.3":"Tattha kalankato santo, ","tha-ap500:15.4":"brahmalokamagacchaham. ","tha-ap500:16.1":"Yavatayum vasitvana, ","tha-ap500:16.2":"tidive upapajjaham; ","tha-ap500:16.3":"Asitikkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap500:16.4":"devarajjamakarayim. ","tha-ap500:17.1":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap500:17.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap500:17.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap500:17.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap500:18.1":"Sonnakinkanipupphanam, ","tha-ap500:18.2":"vipakam anubhomaham; ","tha-ap500:18.3":"Dhatisatasahassani, ","tha-ap500:18.4":"parivarenti mam bhave. ","tha-ap500:19.1":"Thupassa paricinnatta, ","tha-ap500:19.2":"rajojallam na limpati; ","tha-ap500:19.3":"Gatte seda na muccanti, ","tha-ap500:19.4":"suppabhaso bhavamaham. ","tha-ap500:20.1":"Aho me sukato thupo, ","tha-ap500:20.2":"sudittha marika nadi; ","tha-ap500:20.3":"Thupam katvana pulinam, ","tha-ap500:20.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap500:21.1":"Kusalam kattukamena, ","tha-ap500:21.2":"jantuna saragahina; ","tha-ap500:21.3":"Natthi khettam akhettam va, ","tha-ap500:21.4":"patipattiva sadhaka. ","tha-ap500:22.1":"Yathapi balava poso, ","tha-ap500:22.2":"annavam taritussahe; ","tha-ap500:22.3":"Parittam katthamadaya, ","tha-ap500:22.4":"pakkhandeyya mahasaram. ","tha-ap500:23.1":"Imaham kattham nissaya, ","tha-ap500:23.2":"tarissami mahodadhim; ","tha-ap500:23.3":"Ussahena viriyena, ","tha-ap500:23.4":"tareyya udadhim naro. ","tha-ap500:24.1":"Tatheva me katam kammam, ","tha-ap500:24.2":"parittam thokakanca yam; ","tha-ap500:24.3":"Tam kammam upanissaya, ","tha-ap500:24.4":"samsaram samatikkamim. ","tha-ap500:25.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap500:25.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap500:25.3":"Savatthiyam pure jato, ","tha-ap500:25.4":"mahasale suaddhake. ","tha-ap500:26.1":"Saddha mata pita mayham, ","tha-ap500:26.2":"buddhassa saranam gata; ","tha-ap500:26.3":"Ubho ditthapada ete, ","tha-ap500:26.4":"anuvattanti sasanam. ","tha-ap500:27.1":"Bodhipapatikam gayha, ","tha-ap500:27.2":"sonnathupamakarayum; ","tha-ap500:27.3":"Sayam patam namassanti, ","tha-ap500:27.4":"sakyaputtassa sammukha. ","tha-ap500:28.1":"Uposathamhi divase, ","tha-ap500:28.2":"sonnathupam viniharum; ","tha-ap500:28.3":"Buddhassa vannam kittenta, ","tha-ap500:28.4":"tiyamam vitinamayum. ","tha-ap500:29.1":"Saha disvanaham thupam, ","tha-ap500:29.2":"sarim pulinacetiyam; ","tha-ap500:29.3":"Ekasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap500:29.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap500:30.1":"Dvavisatimam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap500:31.1":"Gavesamano tam viram, ","tha-ap500:31.2":"dhammasenapatiddasam; ","tha-ap500:31.3":"Agara nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap500:31.4":"pabbajim tassa santike. ","tha-ap500:32.1":"Jatiya sattavassena, ","tha-ap500:32.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","tha-ap500:32.3":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","tha-ap500:32.4":"gunamannaya cakkhuma. ","tha-ap500:33.1":"Darakeneva santena, ","tha-ap500:33.2":"kiriyam nitthitam maya; ","tha-ap500:33.3":"Katam me karaniyajja, ","tha-ap500:33.4":"sakyaputtassa sasane. ","tha-ap500:34.1":"Sabbaverabhayatito, ","tha-ap500:34.2":"sabbasangatigo isi; ","tha-ap500:34.3":"Savako te mahavira, ","tha-ap500:34.4":"sonnathupassidam phalam. ","tha-ap500:35.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap500:35.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap500:35.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap500:36.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap500:36.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap500:36.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap500:37.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap500:37.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap500:37.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap500:38.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pulinathupiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap500:39.1":"Pulinathupiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}